+## 🔐 The CompTIA Verb Cipher (Bloom's Taxonomy Decoder)
+**Source:** *CompTIA CTT+ Certified Technical Trainer Guide (Table 8-1)*
+**Purpose:** To instantly determine the required study depth ("Flashcard" vs. "Lab") for any N10-009 objective.
+
+### 📜 How to Use This File
