+| 4 | **3D Coordinate Schema** | Designed | Lens (Tree) x Tool (5.5) x Method (5.1). VLAN example validated. |
+| 5 | **Dependency Maps** | Drafted | Full Stack map for 5.2/5.3/5.4 prerequisites. |
