+
+*   **[Previous Net+ Analysis](https://notebooklm.google.com/notebook/9784526e-20fc-4544-86ac-291198ee91bc)**  
+    `https://notebooklm.google.com/notebook/9784526e-20fc-4544-86ac-291198ee91bc`  
+    A pre-engineered "Meta-Language" pipeline designed to parse raw Cengage textbook chapters into operational study assets without manual processing.
+    *   **The Core:** Built on the Conversation Archival Framing Protocol (CAFP), ensuring zero context loss and preventing AI hallucination during data extraction.
+    *   **The Output:** Automates the creation of:
+        *   **Gap Analysis:** Cross-references textbook content against Official N10-009 Objectives to find missing topics.
+        *   **Lab Scenarios:** Auto-generates specific "Level 2" configuration tasks for Proxmox, TrueNAS, and pfSense based on chapter theory.
+        *   **Anki Decks:** Extracts "Flashcard Tier" concepts (ports, protocols, acronyms) into CSV-ready formats.
 
